infrastructure:
I-Geo sisixhobo esinamandla sokubeka iliso kulwakhiwo kunye nokugcinwa kweziseko ezingundoqo kunye nezibonelelo, ngakumbi kwiindawo apho intswela-ngqesho kulutsha iphezulu kwaye urhwaphilizo lunokuba ngumba. Nge-Geo, banokulandela inkqubela phambili kunye nomgangatho ngexesha langempela, baqinisekise ukuba iiprojekthi zigqitywa ngexesha kunye nohlahlo lwabiwo-mali, kwaye bachonge kwaye balungise imiba enokubakho ngaphambi kokuba ibe yingxaki enkulu.
Ngokusebenzisa amandla okubeka iliso kwi-multimedia ye-Geo, i-arhente inokuphucula ukungafihli kunye nokuphendula, okunokunceda ukulwa urhwaphilizo kunye nokwakha ukuthembana noluntu.
Ekugqibeleni, i-Geo inokunceda i-arhente ikhulise impembelelo yotyalo-mali kwiziseko ezingundoqo kunye nezinye izibonelelo, ngelixa idala amathuba olutsha olungaphangeliyo ukuba luthathe inxaxheba ekubekeni iliso kunye negalelo kuphuhliso loluntu lwabo.
govt:
Iiarhente zikarhulumente kunye namagosa anokuzuza kwiGeo ngeendlela ezininzi. Okokuqala, i-Geo inokunceda ekulawuleni ngokufanelekileyo nangempumelelo kwiiprojekthi zeziseko zophuhliso ngokubonelela ngeliso lexesha langempela le-multimedia yokubeka iliso kunye nokunika ingxelo, enokukunceda ukuchonga nokujongana nayo nayiphi na imiba enokuthi ivele ngexesha leprojekthi. Okwesibini, iGeo inokunceda ekulweni urhwaphilizo ngokuvelisa ingxelo enenjongo neqinisekisiweyo yenkqubela yeprojekthi kunye neendleko, ezinokunceda ekuthinteleni okanye ekuboneni izenzo zobuqhophololo.
Okwesithathu, i-Geo inokubonelela ngengqiqo ebalulekileyo kwiimfuno kunye nezinto eziphambili zoluntu, ezinokunceda ii-arhente zikarhulumente ukuba zijolise ngcono kwizibonelelo zabo kunye nemigudu apho zifuneka khona kakhulu. Okokugqibela, ngokuzibandakanya kunye nokuxhobisa abantu abatsha kwinkqubo yokubeka iliso kunye nokunika ingxelo kwiiprojekthi zeziseko ezingundoqo, iGeo inokunceda ukwakha ingqiqo yobunini kunye noxanduva phakathi kolutsha, ngelixa ikwabonelela ngezakhono ezixabisekileyo kunye namava anokunceda ukuphucula amathuba abo engqesho. .
community:
Amaqela oluntu anokuzibandakanya kunye ne-Geo ngokusebenzisa iqonga lokubeka iliso kunye nokulawula iiprojekthi zabo ezisekelwe kuluntu, njengamaphulo okucoca uluntu, amanyathelo okuzithandela, okanye iziganeko zokunyusa imali. Iqonga lingasetyenziselwa ukulandelela inkqubela yezi projekthi nokuqinisekisa ukuba izibonelelo zabiwa ngokufanelekileyo. Ukongeza, amaqela oluntu angasebenzisa i-Geo ukuchaza iziganeko okanye imiba kwindawo abahlala kuyo, njengolwaphulo-mthetho okanye iingozi zendalo, kunye nokulandelela impendulo yabasemagunyeni abafanelekileyo.
Oku kunokunceda ukuphucula ukhuseleko loluntu kunye nokukhuthaza intsebenziswano enkulu phakathi kwamalungu oluntu kunye nee-arhente zorhulumente wendawo. Ekugqibeleni, amaqela oluntu angasebenzisa i-Geo ukulungelelanisa imizamo yokuvolontiya ngexesha likaxakeka, njengeentlekele zendalo, kunye nokuqinisekisa ukuba izibonelelo zisasazwa kwabo basweleyo.
youth:
Ngenxa yokuxhaphaka kwee-smartphones kunye nokusetyenziswa kwemidiya yedijithali phakathi kwabantu abatsha, i-Geo ingaba sisixhobo esibalulekileyo sokubandakanya kunye nokuqesha ulutsha kwiiprojekthi zophuhliso loluntu. Izikhundla zabasebenzi basemasimini zinokujoliswa ngokuthe ngqo kulutsha olukhululekileyo ukusebenzisa ii-smartphones kunye nemidiya yedijithali, kwaye ngubani na okade engaphangeli. Ngaphaya koko, ukubandakanyeka kwi-Geo kunokubonelela ulutsha ngezakhono zomsebenzi ezixabisekileyo kunye namava omsebenzi, anokwandisa ukuqesheka kwabo kwixa elizayo.
Ukongeza, ngokuzibandakanya nolutsha kunye nokubabandakanya kwiiprojekthi zophuhliso loluntu, i-Geo inokunceda ukukhuthaza ukuzingca kunye nobunini kwiindawo abahlala kuzo, ezinokuthi zikhokelele ekwandeni kokubandakanyeka kunye nokuthatha inxaxheba kwixesha elizayo.
